title: Percussion Concert
caption: March 10th
description: The Percussion Concert will be held on March 10th, at the Fresno State concert hall, and will feature all percussion ensembles at UHS. The concert begins at 7:00 PM. Again, it will be at the Fresno State concert hall. If you have any questions, please contact Dr. Cornelison.

title: ACADEC State
caption: March 11th
description: The Academic Decathlon State Competition will be held on March 11th, 2023 in the UHS Computer Lab. Our ACADEC team will be testing all day, so please be quiet as you're walking through the halls. Best of luck!

title: Boys Volleyball

description: Good luck to our Boys Volleyball team as they play for the championship on March 14th, 2023 at Duncan Polytechnical High School. For any questions or well wishes, please see Mr. Hagen!
